&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;Don&#39;t see what you are looking for?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Apply here to be added to our talent pool for future job openings that match your profile and career interests. Should a role open up that aligns with your experience, we’ll be in touch. We also strongly encourage you to follow us on our socials and keep an eye on nexamp.com/careers for future opportunities that spark your interest.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we do:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re a clean energy company working to make solar the easiest, most affordable energy choice. Our end-to-end capabilities—including project development and acquisition, design, construction, operations, and customer management—enable us to serve everyone from global enterprises to individual consumers with unmatched efficiency and reliability. With more than 1 GW of renewable energy-generating assets currently in operation or under construction, we&#39;re building a cleaner and more resilient energy future that works for everyone, and have been for nearly two decades. Headquartered in Boston and Chicago, we’re committed to serving communities nationwide.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you thrive in moments of urgency, growth, and impact, we want you with us.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Team overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Accounting &amp;amp; Finance:&lt;/strong&gt; Oversees accounting, financial planning and reporting, internal controls, cash management, and banking relationships, supporting budgeting, forecasting, and capital decisions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Asset Management:&lt;/strong&gt; Manages Nexamp’s owned and operated solar and storage assets to ensure optimal performance across all portfolios.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Development:&lt;/strong&gt; Expands Nexamp’s distributed solar and storage pipeline through market outreach, site origination, landowner engagement, and lease negotiation.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Capital Markets:&lt;/strong&gt; Leads capital raising efforts, investor relationships, and project- and portfolio-level investment diligence.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Channel Development: &lt;/strong&gt;Acquires fully developed community solar and storage projects prior to construction.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clean Energy Deployment (CED):&lt;/strong&gt; Manages the end-to-end delivery of solar and storage projects, from planning and engineering through construction and interconnection.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clean Energy Operations (CEO):&lt;/strong&gt; Operates and maintains solar and storage assets to maximize energy production, financial performance, and long-term reliability.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Customer Experience &amp;amp; Operations:&lt;/strong&gt; Supports community solar customers with seamless onboarding, subscription management, and ongoing service.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Legal:&lt;/strong&gt; Provides strategic, practical legal guidance to protect Nexamp’s interests and support business objectives.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Marketing, Brand &amp;amp; Enrollment:&lt;/strong&gt; Drives demand through brand storytelling, performance marketing, and customer lifecycle campaigns.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
