&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;Nexamp is seeking to hire a Junior Control Room Operator to join it&#39;s 24/7 Operations Center in Lawrence, MA. In this role, you will be responsible for the real-time monitoring and basic remote operations of Nexamp&#39;s fleet of distributed solar and battery energy storage assets to ensure safe, reliable and optimized performance 365 days a year. You will identify and triage alarms and events, execute standard troubleshooting protocols and escalate issues to the appropriate internal and external stakeholders.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This role is a full time, expected to work 40 hours throughout the week, including weekends &amp;amp; holidays. You will be expected to work a 8 hour shift between the hours of &lt;strong&gt;6am-10pm ET, &lt;/strong&gt;which will be determined upon hire.&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;This role is full time out of our Lawrence, MA Operations Center. You will report to the Manager, Operations Center.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
