&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review, analyze, and interpret utility pre-screen reports, System Impact Studies, Interconnection Service Agreements, and utility negotiations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Witness test procedure review, code interpretation, protective settings development&lt;/li&gt;
